<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.7">
<l>ceṅkamala nāṇmalarmēṟ ṟēṉukaru maṉṉampōṟ</l>
<l>ceṅkaṭ karumēṉi vācutē vaṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>aṅkait talamēṟi yaṉṉa vacañceyyuñ</l>
<l>caṅkaraiyā vaṉcelvañ cāla vaḻakiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O king among conches who climb on the beautiful palm of</l>
<l>red-eyed, dark-bodied Vāsudeva and have a post-meal nap,</l>
<l>just as the swan that enjoys honey does upon the fresh red lotus flower!</l>
<l>Your wealth is very beautiful!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
